-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">，</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">积极开展社会实践活动</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">，</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">推进和落实大学生创新创业教育</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">等要求。</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-10-31%2015%3A12%3A28%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%203.png?Expires=2014096348&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=zND4jAzIuiWN5IndoLtifZn%2BI9c%3D" alt="" width="650" height="762" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">江延湖指出，</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">党</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">支部主题党日作为党内政治生活的一项基础制度，是落实全面从严管党治党，强化党员党性修养的有效抓手</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">。</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">党员同志们要认真学习贯彻习近平总书记考察江西重要讲话精神，并将其落到实处</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">。</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">教师党员们更要坚守自身岗位、共同发力，深度挖掘红色资源、丰富教学形式，做好学生帮扶工作、改善育人环境，把学校教育工作建设好。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">一直以来，学校党委坚持把党支部建设作为最重要的基本建设，树立党的一切工作到支部的鲜明导向，不断优化党支部设置，出台了一系列支部组织工作相关制度。今年，各基层党组织按照学校党委要求，陆续组织开展了主题明确、效果显著的主题党日活动，并将评选出一批主题鲜明、富有成效、值得推广的优秀</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">“主题党日”活动，发挥示范引领作用，切实增强党支部的吸引力、凝聚力和战斗力。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>